1010001.desc: Featuring a sleek design made from waterproof materials, it looks ready to split the waves at any time.
1010001.name: Wavesplitter

1010002.desc: Featuring a sleek design made from waterproof materials, it looks ready to split the waves at any time.
1010002.name: Mega-sized Potato Chips

1010003.desc: A faint light flows between the veins of the leaves. Light and comfortable, it is as if you carry the spirits of nature by your side.
1010003.name: Fairy's Travel Bag

1010004.desc: An eraser that is always trying to roll away. Gotta put this naughty, naughty eraser on a leash.
1010004.name: Naughty Eraser

1010005.desc: An ocean-colored floatie that bounces up and down energetically, inviting you to jump into the sea.
1010005.name: Floatie Buddy

1010006.desc: This soft, fluffy hug pillow seems to sway gently in response to your movements, ready to whisk you away into the land of slumber at any moment.
1010006.name: Nappy Hug Pillow

1010007.desc: An all-natural cosmetic made of woven grass. Fit for a refreshing summer day.
1010007.name: Hay Bale Shadow

1010008.desc: This back-worn guitar emits a few light notes, as though it's improvising a carefree song.
1010008.name: Improv Guitar

1010009.desc: It doesn't draw shapes, but rather the most elegant and orderly ideas.
1010009.name: Creative Compass

1010010.desc: A multipurpose wrench for fixing all sorts of machines. It lets you readily check if any equipment around you needs its screws tightened.
1010010.name: Fixing Wrench

1010011.desc: An antique, giant pocket watch that precisely counts the seconds with ticks and tocks. It's like time is whispering right into your ear.
1010011.name: Ticking Clock

1020001.desc: Stray bits of shipgirl rigging, floating with the waves. I guess they technically also count as... a floating gun.
1020001.name: Floating Gun

1020002.desc: A cup of piping-hot ramen. For once, these chewy noodles taste like pure vacation relaxation.
1020002.name: Cup Ramen

1020003.desc: A lush lotus leaf, casting its mottled green shadow at just the right height.
1020003.name: Green Lotuslight

1020004.desc: A short, thick pencil that slowly traces through the air around you. It's pretending to be real busy, but it's definitely just slacking off.
1020004.name: Wandering Pencil

1020005.desc: A transparent companion that changes the way it floats to match your rhythm. It sometimes bumps into you because it gets curious!
1020005.name: Stealthy Companion

1020006.desc: Ambiguous symbols that continue to float upwards, invoking the feeling of someone who just doesn't want to fully wake up.
1020006.name: Groggy Bubbles

1020007.desc: Let your body move to the rhythm and dance with this hat-wearing cactus!
1020007.name: Jiggy Cactus

1020008.desc: Thick textbooks that turn the pages by themselves. They'll keep floating in front of you until you finish reading them!
1020008.name: Classic Books

1020009.desc: A stuffed toolbox that rattles as you shake it. Got unexpected trouble? Don't worry, it's got a tool to handle every situation.
1020009.name: Utility Box

1020010.desc: A bouquet of blue star flowers that gives off a faint aroma. It gracefully floats beside you, imbuing your every step with a hint of classic romance.
1020010.name: Bouquet for the Stars

1030001.desc: With each step you take, a splash of crystal-clear water springs forth, evoking the refreshing and lively feeling of a seaside stroll.
1030001.name: Trail of Splashing Waves

1030002.desc: With each step you take, ebullient broth and savory soup gushes forth.
1030002.name: Trail of Fragrant Broth

1030003.desc: You leave behind damp footprints with each step you take, like treading along a forest path still glistening with morning dew.
1030003.name: Mossy Steps

1030004.desc: With a stroke of brush, multi-colored note-cats spring to life, composing a cheerful, colorful musical opus.
1030004.name: Trail of Musical Kitties

1030005.desc: The seaspray falls like shimmering snowflakes, leaving a trail of ice that glows in the azure seabreeze with each step you take.
1030005.name: Trail of Frosty Seaspray

1030006.desc: As you wade through the cosmos, the round stars yawn and awaken their brilliance.
1030006.name: Trail of Slumbering Stars

1030007.desc: Riding on horseback with dust and campfire stories on our coats, we head toward the warm lights and commotion.
1030007.name: Traveler's Homecoming

1030008.desc: With each step, you carve rational calculations and logic into the earth.
1030008.name: Calculated Steps

1030009.desc: The flawless gears turn and turn, working around the clock even on holidays.
1030009.name: Tuned Clockwork

1030010.desc: Let blue and white guiding iris flowers mark your wake, engraving a noble coat of arms into your every elegant step.
1030010.name: Iris Emblem

1040001.desc: Clean, sharp lines outline a cool, composed demeanor, perfect for conveying decisiveness and fortitude.
1040001.name: Cool

1040002.desc: Naturally tousled bangs suit styles that pursue lightness and vitality.
1040002.name: Fresh

1040003.desc: Classic side-swept styling reveals a steady demeanor, perfect for crafting a composed and confident image.
1040003.name: Quiet

1050001.desc: A dreamy expression conveys yearning for ideals, fitting for free-spirited or unconventional atmospheres.
1050001.name: Daydreaming

1050002.desc: Gritted teeth and focused, unyielding eyes express persistence and effort.
1050002.name: Grit Teeth

1050003.desc: A mischievous, upturned mouth conveys playfulness and charm, perfect for showcasing a lively, cheeky side.
1050003.name: Cat's Smile

1050004.desc: A serene countenance radiates warmth and approachability, ideal for conveying gentleness.
1050004.name: Gentle

1050005.desc: Sharp gaze, radiating focus and resolve, perfect for conveying decisiveness and presence.
1050005.name: Sharp

1050006.desc: Reserved eyes, cool and unassuming, ideal for portraying depth and steadiness.

1060001.desc: A uniform that blends classic design with comfort, suitable for all daily activities and occasions.

1060002.desc: A set of elegant and refined white formalwear, perfect for any formal occasion.

1060003.desc: Pajamas that are comfortable and easy on the skin, making it easier for your to fall asleep and improving sleep quality.

1060009.desc: Loose collar, airy trousers, a vest, and some firearm accessories. Just one glance tells people that you're a rancher who rides freely and lives life on your own terms.

2010001.desc: A backpack that resembles a small rocket, decorated with a simple mechanical pattern on its surface. With this equipped to your back, you're ready to blast off wherever, whenever!
2010001.name: Rocket Pack

2010002.desc: A standard school backpack. It has a square-shaped exterior with practical compartments that can keep the contents neat and tidy even when the wearer is running and jumping about.
2010002.name: School Backpack

2010003.desc: A backpack in the design of a hand-woven fish basket, exuding the rustic charms of the seaside.
2010003.name: The Joys of Fishing

2010004.desc: A ribbon repurposed into a pair of wings. The wearer might take off like a butterfly at any moment.

2020001.desc: Fluffy clouds drift lazily cross the sky, slow changing shapes in the breeze.

2020002.desc: Small balloons that sway with the wind, leaving joyous trails of color in the deep blue sky.
2020002.name: Breezy Balloon

2020003.desc: Shells float beneath the warm light, shimmering as they trace graceful arcs through the air.

2020004.desc: Your steps shimmer with transparent bubbles, reflecting a dreamy glow beneath the daylight.

2020005.desc: A light and easy-to-use duster. Chang Feng's favorite cleaning tool.

2030003.desc: Leaves behind sticky trails of sweetness with each step, the hexagonal honeycombs glimmering with golden light.
2030003.name: Honeycomb Trail

2030004.desc: Cherry blossom petals dance in the wind, blooming into a gentle spring rain.
2030004.name: Trail of Dancing Cherry Blossoms

2030005.desc: You weave through white waves, leaving trails of shimmering fish.

2030006.desc: Give your steps a delicate lace imprint, like the frills of a maid's dress snuck away and hid under your shoes.
